```class Solution {
    public int minSwaps(int[] nums) {
        int n = nums.length;
        int ones = 0, left = 0, res = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (nums[i] == 1) ones++;
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (nums[i] == 1) {
                left++;
                if (left > ones) {
                    res++;
                    left--;
                }
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
